    "body": "I've thought about almost exactly this feature in the past as well. I would also be interested in having two columns with input and output cells in each. Just like the current structure but in two columns. There's an unnecessary amount of scrolling to find things in the notebook right now that could be mitigated by creating some nonlinear, column-based layout. There are also sorts of issues with this idea which I haven't really ironed out yet but it might be interesting to experiment with.\n"
